race.description: Betdeluxe Same Race Multi 5Th Grade H
race.comment: CAMBLA DIVA (1) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey having won three of three starts. Comes off a (23.92) win last time, scoring by 7 lengths in a Grade 6 over 407m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. BRIGHT SIDE (2) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (24.13) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 407m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Leading player again. UNTAMED RUPEE (8) is a progressive dog who scored his 2nd career win last time at this track, scoring by a nose (24.10). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected again. RUPEE RANGER (7) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
